{
  "stem": "10644.3",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But when I-- it came, you know-- came, you know, to termination of this pregnancy, I called him and he said, I cannot come.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I understand he was a womanizer, tremendous womanizer with the Latvian-- Latvian women.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was very happy that he has now a gynecologist.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "If something happens to these women, he will have a man who will terminate the pregnancy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, it was not [? fetal-- ?] if you have an abortion, it is usually in the first three months.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But for example, I had-- let me-- I will give you an example, a classical example.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A classic example-- a German Jewish woman from my camp, from our camp, comes to me and she says, I'm pregnant.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I examine her.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She's six months pregnant.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I say, tell me where, why did you work?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I knew already that she had some relations with the German who managed this group of people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not a Jew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Floor ?] [? arbiter, ?] you know, it is-- he didn't work.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He only supervised-- supervisor.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And probably with him, she became pregnant.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "She somehow-- I don't know why-- she was hiding.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But six months, she came to me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I say, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] all right, we will have to terminate.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And that was not-- not an abortion.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That I had to induce labor.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, that is-- I dilated the cervix.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I ruptured the membranes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I had between-- [INAUDIBLE] to stimulate the uterus.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I brought to-- she had contractions.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She had labor.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she expelled the fetus.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The fetus was-- I don't-- you don't care.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't care what it is.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it is--",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When it weighs 600 grams, you know, what do I care?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I am in a concentration camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know the results.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I know the results that she-- if the baby is alive, and she's alive, they both will be killed.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know what my sanitator, you know, did, you know?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Probably went somewhere and buried-- buried them in the premises of this-- of this-- compound.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Hold on, I didn't finish.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She was starting to get a little temperature.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I decided to keep here for one, two days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't know what is the reason for the temperature.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Maybe she has some TB in the lungs, you know, and a temperature.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But on the second day, or on the third day, I-- someone from the camp comes running to me, Visner is here.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Visner is-- we are now a part of a concentration camp, Riga [NON-ENGLISH] Kaiserwald.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We are a part.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's when the SS people came.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That is everything part of the concentration.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But we were Arbeitslager.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We were working, working, working for their very important part.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They don't have any other workers but Jews to work on the airport to enlarge and maintain.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And Visner was the-- there was-- the doctor of this Kaiserwald was a man with the name Krepsbach.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was in the rank of major in SS, Sturmbannfuhrer-- Sturmbannfuhrer Krepsbach, nickname Dr.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Spritzbach.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Spritz, you know, what means-- injection.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was known-- he was before this, he was in Mauthausen-- Camp Mauthausen.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was with terrible reputation came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He was injecting phenol intravenously, and the terrible pains, which in ten minutes, they were dead.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What?",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
